      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Shawn Chidester</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:221px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/shawn-chidester-62a8b494/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/3f/ShawnChidester.jpg\" width=\"219\" height=\"219\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ShawnChidester.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Shawn Chidester<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Shawn Chidester</b>,<br />\nan American senior software engineer at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Attensity\">Attensity</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nand as computer chess programmer author of the chess engines <a href=\"/index.php?title=CACIO&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"CACIO (page does not exist)\">CACIO</a> (early 90s in <a href=\"/Pascal#TurboPascal\" title=\"Pascal\">Turbo Pascal</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>), \n<a href=\"/Clubfoot\" title=\"Clubfoot\">Clubfoot</a>, its <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> counterpart <a href=\"/Bitfoot\" title=\"Bitfoot\">Bitfoot</a>, the experimental <a href=\"/index.php?title=Clunk&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Clunk (page does not exist)\">Clunk</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bumblebee&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bumblebee (page does not exist)\">Bumblebee</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, and the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Senjo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Senjo (page does not exist)\">Senjo</a> <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> adapter. \nSenjo simplifies the UCI protocol implementation of engines written in C++, as demonstrated by Clubfoot, Bitfoot and Bumblebee <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2015\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2016\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shawn_Chidester&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015\">2015</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shawn_Chidester&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2015\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55734\">Singular extensions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 21, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Singular_Extensions\" title=\"Singular Extensions\">Singular Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55876\">Licensing</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 03, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56142\">Rook vs 2 minor pieces with pawns on the board</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2015 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56312\">LMR tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56625\">Introducing Bitfoot</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 08, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57287\">Razoring vs Futility pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 16, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Razoring</a>, <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57843\">Verification of pruning techniques</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 04, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58725\">Clunk 1.0 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 29, 2015</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016\">2016</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shawn_Chidester&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2016\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59182\">Bumblebee 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 07, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59401\">Transposition table replacement strategies</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 01, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59928\">Test position that requires KKP evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 22, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/KPK\" title=\"KPK\">KPK</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61064\">Calculating space</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 07, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shawn_Chidester&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/shawn-chidester-62a8b494/\">Shawn Chidester | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/zd3nik\">(Shawn Chidester) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/zd3nik/SenjoUCIAdapter\">Senjo C++ UCI Adapter</a> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shawn_Chidester&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/shawn-chidester-62a8b494/\">Shawn Chidester | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pub/shawn-chidester/94/8b4/62a\">Shawn Chidester | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/zd3nik/CACIO\">GitHub - zd3nik/CACIO: My first chess program (created 1994-ish)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58725\">Clunk 1.0 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 29, 2015</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59182\">Bumblebee 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 07, 2016</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/zd3nik/SenjoUCIAdapter\">Senjo C++ UCI Adapter</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301152254\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 107/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 234/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6712-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301152254 and revision id 17034\n -->\n"
